## ğŸ§© React Works Like LEGO Blocks

In React, everything is divided into **components**.

Example:

If you build a food ordering app ğŸ”

You can divide it like this:

* `<Navbar />`
* `<FoodCard />`
* `<Cart />`
* `<Footer />`

Each part is a **component**.

Instead of writing everything in one big file ğŸ˜µ
You break it into small pieces ğŸ˜

That makes your project:

* Clean
* Easy to manage
* Easy to update

